=head1 DESCRIPTION

This shows the summary status of the keyspace after a new Amazon Web
Services Region was added.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> KeyspaceStatus => Str

The status of the keyspace.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Region => Str

The name of the Region that was added to the keyspace.


=head2 TablesReplicationProgress => Str

This shows the replication progress of tables in the keyspace. The
value is expressed as a percentage of the newly replicated tables with
status C<Active> compared to the total number of tables in the
keyspace.



